1. Install cmake (apt-get install cmake)
2. Run cmake pointed to the directory with the source code
$ cmake tools/techcon14-nvram
3. Run make in the directory to build memthrottle target
$ cd tools/techcon14-nvram; make memthrottle
4. Run memthrottle in the background when running your application. It will output the throughput achieved by each of the threads.
$ cd memthrottle; ./memthrottle <number of threads> <target BW per thread>

